      "usage": {
        "en": "This class has been added in the CPSV-AP to complement the need for adding other ways of classifying the Public Service, which have not been explicitly defined in the CPSV-AP. In this context, the CPSV-AP reuses the Concept class as defined in <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/\">the SKOS Simple Knowledge Organization System</a>. For describing the attributes of a Concept (labels, preferred labels, alternative labels, definition, etc.) we refer to <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/\">SKOS</a>. The Concept may or may not belong to (member) a certain Collection."
